short_description.title: Short Description
short_description.content: Experience non-stop excitement with the Aquaventure Dubai Day Pass. Enjoy world-class water slides, the iconic Atlantis Leap of Faith, and serene private beaches. Perfect for a day of thrilling water adventures and relaxation.

label.en: Atlantis Aquaventure Super Pass - (Aquaventure + Lost Chamber)

short_description.title: Short Description
short_description.content: Unlock ultimate fun with the Aquaventure Super Pass! Enjoy unlimited access to thrilling water slides, the Atlantis Leap of Faith, the Lost Chambers Aquarium, and pristine private beaches. Perfect for a full day of adventure and exploration.

label.en: Atlantis the Lost Chamber Aquarium Ticket

short_description.title: Short Description
short_description.content:
• Visit the incredible underwater world of The Lost Chambers Aquarium, home to over 65,000 marine animals that bring the ocean to life.
  • Explore 21 unique marine exhibits on a journey through 14 fascinating chambers.
  • Uncover the secrets of the deep, including the magnificent Ambassador Lagoon, an 11-million-litre aquarium showcasing a stunning array of marine life—perfect for the ultimate Instagram backdrop.

label.en: Atlantis Aquaventure Day Pass + Madame Tussauds Dubai Ticket

short_description.title: Short Description
short_description.content: Enjoy a day of excitement with this combo! Dive into the thrills of Atlantis Aquaventure Waterpark with its exhilarating slides and attractions, then meet your favorite stars at Madame Tussauds Dubai. A perfect mix of water fun and celebrity encounters!

label.en: Atlantis Aquaventure Day Pass + Monorail One Way Gateway to Atlantis Ticket

short_description.title: Short Description
short_description.content: Experience the best of Atlantis with this combo! Start your adventure with a scenic Monorail ride (one-way) to the Gateway to Atlantis, then enjoy a day full of thrills at the Aquaventure Waterpark. A perfect combination of travel and fun!

label.en: Atlantis Aquaventure Day Pass + Monorail Round Trip Gateway to Atlantis Ticket

short_description.title: Short Description
short_description.content: Make the most of your Atlantis visit with this round-trip combo! Enjoy a scenic round-trip Monorail ride to and from the Gateway to Atlantis, then dive into the excitement at Aquaventure Waterpark with a full day of thrilling slides, rides, and attractions. The perfect way to experience both land and water adventures!

label.en: Atlantis Aquaventure Day Pass + Ski Dubai Snow Classic Ticket

short_description.title: Short Description
short_description.content: Enjoy a day of thrills with this combo! Dive into the excitement at Atlantis Aquaventure Waterpark and then experience winter fun with the Ski Dubai Snow Classic Pass, including access to the Snow Park and activities. A perfect mix of water and snow adventures!

label.en: Atlantis Aquaventure Day Pass + Green Planet Ticket

short_description.title: Short Description
short_description.content: Experience two amazing attractions with this combo! Enjoy the thrilling Aquaventure Waterpark at Atlantis, then explore the lush wonders of the Green Planet, Dubai's indoor rainforest. A day full of adventure and nature!

label.en: Atlantis Aquaventure Day Pass + 3D Selfie Museum Ticket

short_description.title: Short Description
short_description.content: Make your day unforgettable with this combo! Splash into fun at Atlantis Aquaventure Waterpark, then strike a pose at the 3D Selfie Museum, where you can interact with incredible optical illusions. A perfect mix of adventure and creativity!

label.en: Atlantis Aquaventure Day Pass + View at the Pam Non-Prime Ticket

short_description.title: Short Description
short_description.content: Enjoy a thrilling day with this combo! Dive into the excitement at Atlantis Aquaventure Waterpark, then take in the stunning views from the Burj Khalifa’s 124th & 125th floors (non-prime hours). A perfect blend of adventure and breathtaking sights!

short_description.title: Short Description
short_description.content: Savor a delicious meal with stunning views from Level 52 during non-prime hours. Enjoy a choice of one main course—either a flavorful pasta or a freshly baked pizza—paired with a delectable dessert. Relax in a scenic setting while indulging in a delightful dining experience. Perfect for a casual yet memorable meal above the city!

label.en: View at the Palm - Dinner with a View

inclusions.title: Inclusions
inclusions.content:
• Prime hours access to Level 52.
  • Choice of 1 main course (pasta or pizza) & 1 dessert.

short_description.title: Short Description
short_description.content: Enjoy a breathtaking dining experience at View at the Palm, where stunning skyline views meet exquisite flavors. Savor a carefully curated dinner with a selection of delectable dishes in an elegant setting. Watch the city lights sparkle as you indulge in a memorable culinary journey. Perfect for a romantic evening or a special night out above Dubai!
